      "content": "that makes sense, but i need to get more specific for my design team. like, if we're looking for that \"authentic\" urban core look, what are the actual visual hallmarks? are we talking certain color palettes, specific types of fabrics, or even certain \"characters\" or archetypes that represent the street vibe? just trying to get a concrete mood board started.",
